'''G18P''' is a [[pigeon rotavirus]] infecting and killing domestic pigeons. This disease is found in [[Western Australia]], Victoria and [[South Australia]].<ref>{{cite web|title=Are Australia's native pigeons sitting ducks?|url=https://phys.org/news/2017-07-australia-native-pigeons-ducks.html|website=Phys.org|accessdate=16 July 2017}}</ref>


